2008-08-03  version 2.0beta1

	* upgrade to xulrunner1.9 (=Firefox3)
	* added support for linux/x86, solarix/x86
	* fixed classloaders problems on OSX Leopard
	* fixed extension manager to work
	* reduce flicker under osx when resizing the widget
	* added methods converting DOM elements to coordinates

2008-08-03  version 1.0

	* equal to 1.0beta1

2008-02-08  version 1.0beta1

	* first public release
	* based on xulrunner1.8  (=Firefox2)
	* support for win32, osx/i386, osx/ppc

